==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-obtain.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|obtain||}}

# {{transitive}}: To [[hold]]; to [[keep]]; to [[possess]].
# {{transitive}}: To get hold of by [[effort]]; to [[gain]] [[possession]] of; to [[procure]]; to [[acquire]], in any way.
# {{transitive}}: To become held; to gain or have a [[firm footing]]; to be [[recognize]]d or [[establish]]ed; to [[subsist]]; to become [[prevalent]] or [[general]]; to [[prevail]]; as, the custom obtains of going to the seashore in summer.
# {{transitive}}: To prevail; to [[succeed]].
# {{intransitive}}: To exist; as, those ideas no longer obtain.

